Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.14,0:00:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么，继续往下读吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我没有听到那个声音.................
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.34,0:00:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们班的班主任
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.26,0:01:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,青井老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.46,0:01:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我向往的女神般的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.55,0:01:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在虽然仅仅是师生关系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.88,0:01:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不择手段也要让她成为我的专属女人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.95,0:01:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为，我是这家学校理事长的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.19,0:01:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有得不到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.27,0:01:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么，今晚你准备干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，马上就要参加文学大会了，我要准备资料
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.12,0:01:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天要晚点回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.52,0:01:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，对了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.54,0:01:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.86,0:01:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请摘下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.06,0:02:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，太粗心了，忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本来，我们都是隐婚的那
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.26,0:02:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为是禁止职场恋爱的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很喜欢的青井老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.84,0:02:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的没想到她居然和一起工作的同事老师结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.59,0:02:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我知道这个事实的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.26,0:02:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我决心全力以赴打败他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.45,0:05:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，你回来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在学校的时候，一直很想做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.82,0:06:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，正因为是新婚最近都完全没有做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩，不是一直非常的忙嘛，那也是没有办法的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想做爱爱的，也不只是你一个人呦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.44,0:06:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.27,0:06:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也正想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.52,0:10:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湿漉漉的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:10:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.52,0:12:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.21,0:12:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.02,0:12:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，来了，来了，来了，来了，来了，啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.34,0:12:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也给我舔舔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.47,0:12:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩，你都帮我舔过了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.51,0:12:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相互舔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.78,0:14:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.44,0:16:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.77,0:16:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩，想插了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.60,0:16:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不了了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.78,0:16:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就这样射可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩，不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.13,0:16:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.91,0:16:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.17,0:16:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩，不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.30,0:16:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.39,0:16:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩？恩？哈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.10,0:16:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿，它还在动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.47,0:17:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.16,0:19:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插在里面舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.21,0:19:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.18,0:19:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，超赞，舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.88,0:20:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈，心情很好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.56,0:20:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩，心情舒畅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.41,0:21:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.04,0:21:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.37,0:21:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很爽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.64,0:21:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚好象快来高潮了是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.93,0:21:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.58,0:21:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没有？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.34,0:21:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.79,0:21:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.45,0:21:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.00,0:21:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝这边，恩，朝这边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.00,0:22:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.23,0:22:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,素空的脸最喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.36,0:22:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.36,0:22:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己在摸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.50,0:22:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在动着的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.67,0:22:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己插插吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.20,0:22:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.72,0:22:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，爽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.10,0:22:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要快点冲撞吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.41,0:22:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.24,0:22:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.18,0:22:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.87,0:22:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.78,0:23:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不嘛，冲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.09,0:23:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,额，不行了，不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.20,0:23:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,额，来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.28,0:23:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,额，来了，来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.78,0:23:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又来了一次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.03,0:23:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爽呦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.41,0:24:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，爽
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.77,0:25:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，爽
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.99,0:25:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.45,0:25:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，不行了，不行了，不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.86,0:25:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，来了，来了，来了，来了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.63,0:25:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，来了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.63,0:25:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,额，不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.08,0:25:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,累瘫了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.11,0:25:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.66,0:25:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,累垮了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.36,0:26:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.72,0:26:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.78,0:26:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，爽
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.49,0:26:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.34,0:26:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.39,0:26:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.79,0:27:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，来了，啊..............
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.13,0:27:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，来了，来了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.70,0:27:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩，领受
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.59,0:28:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.19,0:28:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩，好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.24,0:28:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，射了这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.27,0:28:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈，真的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.72,0:28:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩，去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.68,0:28:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.06,0:28:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.97,0:28:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师，有点事找你，有时间吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.79,0:28:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，这位是理事长的...............                                                                     承蒙你父亲的一直关照
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.03,0:28:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.47,0:29:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.97,0:29:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这所学校应该是严禁职场恋爱的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.19,0:29:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到教师自己都违反规定，这是不容原谅的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.32,0:29:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩，是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.78,0:29:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就象学生如果违反了校规，需要承受惩罚那样
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.21,0:29:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,青井老师也同样，也应该受到惩罚才对
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.85,0:29:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我利用了理事长儿子的身份，决定策划并参加对青井老师的凌辱计划
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.21,0:29:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先从平时开始，就向和她结婚的老师，还有关系不好的老师发放照片
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.30,0:30:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.47,0:30:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,额？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.72,0:30:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准告诉任何人，今天下课后到理事长室报到
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.84,0:31:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的学校可是有名的高中学校
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.62,0:31:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,严禁职场恋爱的，青井老师
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.37,0:31:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这到底算什么？这么过分的事情老师您也...............
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.78,0:31:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是你想的那样哦，青井老师
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.34,0:31:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是受人之托，忠人之事罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.50,0:31:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受人之托？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.49,0:31:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,额
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.50,0:31:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来，来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.64,0:31:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.28,0:31:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请放开我！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.78,0:31:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.73,0:31:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.29,0:31:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请放开我！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.52,0:31:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来，给我坐下！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.22,0:32:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正你违反校规，横竖
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.37,0:32:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是要受到处罚的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.12,0:32:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老实点
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.17,0:32:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我老实点，你也不想你的照片泄露出去吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.76,0:32:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.79,0:32:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你放了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.70,0:32:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别不识抬举
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.77,0:32:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.58,0:32:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.49,0:32:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么，我就把你全绑上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.69,0:32:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.28,0:32:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.09,0:32:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.33,0:32:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来，拍个照片纪念纪念
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.43,0:32:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，不要拍
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.00,0:32:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要拍
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.93,0:32:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘴巴不要讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.72,0:32:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.52,0:33:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.42,0:33:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看这里
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.06,0:33:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.35,0:33:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有了这个，你就不会告诉任何人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.22,0:33:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.92,0:33:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.89,0:33:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.37,0:33:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.50,0:33:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.89,0:33:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是都被他摸了个遍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.05,0:33:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样难道不好吗？真是的，又不会少掉一块肉
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.71,0:33:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我看到了那么色情的照片，就算是我，也欲火难耐呦
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.39,0:33:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.50,0:34:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢这样？还是...............
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.76,0:34:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要，不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.02,0:34:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要碰我！
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.03,0:34:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真诱人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.38,0:34:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说句实话吧，老师
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.45,0:34:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我呢，从很早以前就开始关注着老师你
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.55,0:34:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真没想到居然会天赐良缘那
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.38,0:35:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.50,0:35:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.78,0:35:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不甘心？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.93,0:35:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很伤心？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.68,0:35:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.37,0:35:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剪破了，对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.60,0:35:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,划伤了你的话也对不起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.51,0:35:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.23,0:35:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样不是很好吗？是吧老师
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.58,0:36:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个
