Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.73,0:37:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.09,0:37:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BB
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.84,0:37:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.37,0:37:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BB
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.04,0:37:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变态
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.71,0:37:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,淫乱的教师
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.55,0:37:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么恬不知耻的话也能说的出来
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.28,0:38:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,青井老师你果然变态那
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.49,0:38:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要，不要
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.59,0:38:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.76,0:38:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变态的话，这种东西就不需要了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.98,0:38:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.56,0:38:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可事先告诉你啊
